        "cooked": "<p>You can just <a href=\"https://support.signal.org/hc/en-us/articles/6255134251546-Edit-Message\">edit</a> the message with a <a href=\"https://support.signal.org/hc/en-us/articles/6325622209178-Text-Formatting\">strike through</a>. Or edit the message to say ‚ÄúEdit: resolved‚Äù or whatever is applicable. Or you can quote-reply the ‚Äúobsolete‚Äù message with the resolution.</p>",
